       SELECT POT1-F           ASSIGN   WK-POT1-F-NAME
                               STATUS   WK-POT1-STATUS
           ORGANIZATION LINE   SEQUENTIAL.

       DATA                    DIVISION.
       FILE                    SECTION.

       FD  PIN1-F
           LABEL RECORDS ARE STANDARD
           RECORD VARYING DEPENDING ON WK-PIN1-LEN.
       01  PIN1-REC.
             05  FILLER        PIC  X(1024).

