           LABEL RECORDS ARE STANDARD.
       01  POT1-REC.
           03  FILLER          PIC  X(300).

       WORKING-STORAGE         SECTION.
       01  WORK-AREA.
           03  WK-PGM-NAME     PIC  X(008) VALUE "TEST31  ".

           03  WK-PIN1-F-NAME  PIC  X(032) VALUE
               "TEST28_201110_2018XX.CSV".
